libs.content:
find_program(cppcheck_executable
    names
      cppcheck
      cli
    paths
      "${cppcheck_root_dir}"
    path_suffixes
      cli
    no_default_path)
find_program(clangtidy_executable names clang-tidy-13 clang-tidy-12 clang-tidy-11 clang-tidy-10 clang-tidy-9 clang-tidy-9 clang-tidy-8 clang-tidy)

find_program(w3_executable
      names w3
      doc "web3.storage cli executable"
      required)

find_program(ipfs_executable
          names jsipfs
          doc "interplanetary filesystem (ipfs) executable")

find_program(
  kwstyle_executable
  names kwstyle
  doc "path to the kwstyle executable"
  )

project(nifti         version 0.0.0.0         description "niftilib is a set of i/o libraries for reading and writing files in the nifti-1 data format. nifti-1 is a binary file format for storing medical image data, e.g. magnetic resonance image (mri)

project(vxl #project name must be all caps to have properly generated vxl_version_* variables     version  4.2.1.0 # defines #major,minor,patch,tweak}     description "a multi-platform collection of c++ software libraries for computer vision and image understanding."     languages cxx c)

libs.content: find_program( lcov_path  names lcov lcov.bat lcov.exe lcov.perl)
find_program( genhtml_path names genhtml genhtml.perl genhtml.bat )

find_library(win32sdk_libraries
    names kernel32.lib user32.lib gdi32.lib winspool.lib comdlg32.lib advapi32.lib shell32.lib ole32.lib oleaut32.lib uuid.lib odbc32.lib odbccp32.lib
    paths
      "c:/program files/microsoft sdks/windows"
      "c:/program files (x86)/microsoft sdks/windows"
      "c:/program files (x86)/windows kits/"
    path_suffixes
      "v6.0a/lib"
      "v6.1/lib"
      "v7.0a/lib"
      "v7.1a/lib"
      "8.0/lib/win8/um/x86"
      "10/lib/10.0.17134.0/um/x86"

)
